          <from>MR. JIM BOUDREAU</from>
          <p>MR. JIM BOUDREAU : Mr. Speaker, I beg leave to make an introduction on behalf of the MLA for Truro-Bible Hill. We have a group here today, I believe, in the Speaker's Gallery from Le Centre Communautaire francophone de Truro: Professor Yvette Saulnier and &#xE9;tudiants C&#xE9;line Thimot, Elisabeth Dromer, Peter Betts, and Itsvan Krizan. We want to welcome them to the House today. (Applause)</p>
        </speech>
