      <debateSection>
        <heading>PREM.: MUSKRAT FALLS PROJ. - BUDGET OVERAGES</heading>
        <speech by="#bbf5376f-1a5e-4a10-ac71-5a195ac61a59">
          <from>MR. ANDREW YOUNGER</from>
          <p>MR. ANDREW YOUNGER : Mr. Speaker, my question is for the Premier. Obviously we're happy that after saying that the debate on Muskrat Falls was not necessary this summer, he has finally agreed that debate in this Legislature is necessary.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#0768c045-71ae-4890-b6be-c52eb783ee95">
          <from>THE PREMIER</from>
